four portals open up around Ironraptor postion out steps 
Arcangel,Tritan,Icedemon, and Shocker. They see Ironraptor hurt so they 
surrond her.



Arcangel:



"Shocker help Zardus and Tritan you go after Shockwave. Me and Icedemon will 
fuck up who ever comes after Ironrapator."





Tritan flys up and starts to breath fire all over Shockwave.

and himself and says to Ironraptor"just stay down".


Shocker pulls out his sword and shoves it in the of sixshot and says to 
Zardus "need any help".



Arcangel is holding his side from the last battle.
